readme: ## nan-x The constant NaN derived mathematically by 0 / 0. ### `module.exports` : number ⏏ The constant NaN derived mathematically by 0 / 0. **Kind**: Exported member **Example** ```js import NAN from 'nan-x'; console.log(NAN !== NAN); // true console.log(NAN === NAN); // false ```
